ream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/best-for-seniors\">Seniors</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/kids-and-families\">Kids &amp; Families</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/best-for-gifts\">Gifts</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/premium-picks\">Premium Picks</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/compare\">Compare</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/questions\">Questions?</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"shrink-0 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold transition border-coral-200 bg-cream-50 text-slate-700 hover:border-trust-400 hover:bg-trust-50 hover:text-trust-700\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div></nav></header><main><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://interactivepetmarketplace.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Senior Research\",\"item\":\"https://interactivepetmarketplace.com/senior-research\"}]}</script><section class=\"pt-10 pb-3 sm:pt-12 sm:pb-4 lg:pt-14 lg:pb-5\"><div class=\"container-shell\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">Research</p><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl\">Research on Interactive Pets and Senior Wellbeing</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600\">A growing body of research suggests that interactive and robotic pets can meaningfully improve the lives of seniors — especially those facing loneliness, isolation, dementia, depression, or anxiety.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-2\"><div class=\"container-shell max-w-4xl\"><a class=\"block group\" href=\"/senior-research/summaries\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-trust-700 group-hover:text-trust-900 underline\">Articles on the Effect of Interactive Pets on Seniors</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-xl font-bold underline text-slate-700 group-hover:text-slate-900\">(Click to see summaries of articles.)</p></a></div></section><section class=\"pt-6 pb-10 sm:pt-8 sm:pb-12\"><div class=\"container-shell\"><ol class=\"space-y-6 list-decimal pl-6 max-w-4xl\"><li class=\"text-slate-700\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\" href=\"https://www.aarp.org/caregiving/basics/robotic-companion-animals/\">“<!-- -->Studies Show Benefits of Robotic Pets for Loved Ones With Dementia, Loneliness<!-- -->”</a><span class=\"text-slate-600\"> — <!-- -->AARP</span></li><li class=\"text-slate-700\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\" href=\"https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC8082946/\">“<!-- -->Impacts of Low-cost Robotic Pets for Older Adults<!-- -->”</a><span class=\"text-slate-600\"> — <!-- -->National Institutes of Health / PMC</span></li><li class=\"text-slate-700\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\" href=\"https://academic.oup.com/psychsocgerontology/article/75/9/2018/5891953\">“<!-- -->Robotic Pet Use Among Community-Dwelling Older Adults<!-- -->”</a><span class=\"text-slate-600\"> — <!-- -->Oxford Academic</span></li><li class=\"text-slate-700\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\" href=\"https://wellbeings.org/well-beings-x-forbes-robotic-pets-can-dramatically-improve-the-lives-of-older-adults-with-dementia-and-depression/\">“<!-- -->Robotic Pets Can Dramatically Improve the Lives of Older Adults With Dementia and Depression<!-- -->”</a><span class=\"text-slate-600\"> — <!-- -->Forbes / Well Beings</span></li><li class=\"text-slate-700\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\" href=\"https://www.ajgponline.org/article/S1064-7481(25)00558-5/fulltext\">“<!-- -->Effect of a Robot Pet Companion on the Mood of Older Adults<!-- -->”</a><span class=\"text-slate-600\"> — <!-- -->PubMed / American Journal of Geriatric Psychiatry</span></li><li class=\"text-slate-700\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\" href=\"https://www.jamda.com/article/S1525-8610(24)00176-2/fulltext\">“<!-- -->Effect of Social Robots on Depression and Loneliness<!-- -->”</a><span class=\"text-slate-600\"> — <!-- -->ScienceDirect / JAMDA</span></li><li class=\"text-slate-700\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\" href=\"https://www.pacificneuroscienceinstitute.org/blog/brain-health/robotic-pets-provide-comfort-to-dementia-patients/\">“<!-- -->Robotic Pets Provide Comfort to Dementia Patients<!-- -->”</a><span class=\"text-slate-600\"> — <!-- -->Pacific Neuroscience Institute</span></li><li class=\"text-slate-700\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\" href=\"https://www.wired.com/review/elliq-ai-companion-robot/\">“<!-- -->ElliQ AI Companion Robot Review<!-- -->”</a><span class=\"text-slate-600\"> — <!-- -->WIRED</span></li><li class=\"text-slate-700\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\" href=\"https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fpsyg.2023.1106633/full\">“<!-- -->Companion Robots to Mitigate Loneliness Among Older Adults<!-- -->”</a><span class=\"text-slate-600\"> — <!-- -->Frontiers in Psychology</span></li><li class=\"text-slate-700\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\" href=\"https://academic.oup.com/gerontologist/article/65/12/gnaf219/8268528\">“<!-- -->Wired for Companionship<!-- -->”</a><span class=\"text-slate-600\"> — <!-- -->The Gerontologist / Oxford Academic</span></li></ol><div class=\"mt-10 text-center\"><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 sm:text-sm\">Last updated: <time dateTime=\"2026-05-17\">2026-05-17</time></p></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"border-t border-coral-200 bg-cream-100\"><div class=\"container-shell py-12\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><p class=\"text-base font-semibold text-brand-900\">Interactive Pet Marketplace</p><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-sm text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\">A cleaner way to compare companion-style plushy companions and AI &amp; robotic pets for seniors, families, and gift buyers.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-brand-900\">Explore</p><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600\"><a class=\"block hover:text-brand-700\" href=\"/plushy-companions\">Plushy Companions</a><a class=\"block hover:text-brand-700\" href=\"/a